{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"VideoGame","name":"Steambirds: Survival","description":""SteamBirds: Survival" is a dogfighting strategy game that lets you take on an ever-growing number of enemies until you finally bite the dust. It is the sequel to the hit game "Steambirds", designed by Andy Moore (aka "Weasello") and Daniel Cook, which was played by over 10m people worldwide.

SB:S on Kongregate features 16 distinct planes, each of which have unique strengths and weakness that emphasize different play styles. Each plane has its own local and global leaderboard, so you can pick your favorite then fight to distinguish yourself as the master of that plane!

How long can you last against an endless onslaught of enemies? A million lives depend on the answer to that question!","image":"https://cdn2.kongcdn.com/game_icons/0019/5253/kong.png?i10c=img.resize(width:240,height:191)","aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"4.08368","ratingCount":15881,"bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1"},"applicationCategory":"Strategy, Plane, Turn Based, Flight, War, Steampunk, Upgrades, Top Down, Army, Good Music, Historical, Airport, Atmospheric, Defense, Team, Bird, Farm, Time Management","creator":{"@type":"Organization","name":"spryfox","logo":"https://cdn3.kongcdn.com/user_avatars/0445/2826/SpryFox_logo.png?i10c=img.resize(width:28)"}}
